{"tid":255957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IT業成被炒魷高危陷低潮？調查報告唔係咁講","createTime":"2017-05-24T07:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T07:46:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62ce649876a3a2e6fdc6334074c5214af52bdae3","tid":255957,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495610798_005b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495610798_005b.jpg&h=137702cb&s={SIZE}\" />     <br />\n<br />\n國泰航空日前宣佈裁減600人，IT部門屬重災區，但有調查發現，本港僱主對IT人才極為渴求。職業訓練局屬下資訊科技訓練發展委員會今日發表「2016年資訊科技業人力調查報告」，報告預計現時至2020年，行業每年需增聘近5,200名生力軍，配合行業發展。<br />\n<br />\n調查於2016年4月至5月期間進行，抽樣訪問1,628間機構。調查顯示，資訊科技業的僱員人數，在過去十年持續增長，由2004年約62,000人，上升至去年接近 88,000人，增加逾四成。其中通訊服務業的資訊科技僱員人數，於2016年錄得顯著升幅，較上一次調查2014年上升33.2%，相信是受惠於本地互聯網及通訊服務的技術持續優化，帶動相關行業人手需求增加。<br />\n<br />\n調查又顯示，約7,000名僱員在過去12月內曾轉職，其中以從事建造業的僱員流動率最高(12.3%)，其次是數碼創意業(11.1%)。人力調查工作小組召集人蒙美玲教授表示，不同機構對資訊科技人手需求均持續上升，反映行業前景樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n委員會亦指出數據科學、大數據及數據分析是業界專才所需十大技術之一。數據分析透過分析重要數據，協助各行各業作出更有效的營商方案，提升競爭力。"},{"pid":"f454df4087c208c1125f4b5d671034b340296ddb","tid":255957,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56735871&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56735871%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&d=aH8KaMvKRe05vg3cyv5gNoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=c3fd4f64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56735871%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&h=06340445\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56735871&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524</a>"},{"pid":"9562a89e68cef78c7f89da4a9550a8bd9d61a164","tid":255957,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"個個得個UP字<br />\n有幾得公司有本事同有咁多資料搞大數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab2bb1f5ffc924395a325df9e6e19bf93b42091","tid":255957,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}